title: The Breakfast Club Talks Kamala Harris, Rumors, and Naked Massages
itunes:title: The Breakfast Club Talks Kamala Harris, Rumors, and Naked Massages
description:
Today on The Breakfast Club Angela Yee breaks down Kamala Harris' new interview with CBS during Front Page News and during Rumor Report we find out why Ne-yo didn't sign new artist Lucky Daye. Charlamagne gives today's Donkey of The Day and we ask the callers if they wear underwear or go commando when it comes to getting massages
